msgctxt "80_Haruka"
msgid "You're going back to Kamurocho, aren't you?"
msgstr "Volverás a Kamurocho, ¿no?"

msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "Haruka, I..."
msgstr "Haruka, Yo..."

msgctxt "116_Haruka"
msgid "I just don't get it, Uncle Kaz. How can you trust him so\\r\n"\n"easily?"
msgstr "Simplemente no lo entiendo, tío Kaz. ¿Cómo puedes confiar en él tan\\r\n"\n"fácilmente?"

msgctxt "128_Haruka"
msgid "He stabbed you in broad daylight, Uncle Kaz! You almost died!"
msgstr "¡Te apuñaló a plena luz del día, tío Kaz! ¡Casi te mueres!"

msgctxt "140_Haruka"
msgid "I'll never trust him... Never in a million years."
msgstr "Nunca confiaré en él... Ni en un millón de años."

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "Haruka, please."
msgstr "Haruka, por favor."

msgctxt "176_Haruka"
msgid "Whenever I see him, I just think back to what happened last\\r\n"\n"year. What he did to you."
msgstr "Siempre que lo veo, solo pienso en lo que pasó el año pasado. En lo que te hizo."

msgctxt "188_Haruka"
msgid "That memory terrifies me, Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Esa memoria me aterra, tío Kaz."

msgctxt "200_Kiryu"
msgid "Haruka..."
msgstr "Haruka..."

msgctxt "212_Haruka"
msgid "I've always believed in you. You know I have."
msgstr "Siempre he creído en ti. Sabes que lo he hecho."

msgctxt "224_Haruka"
msgid "But this time... I'm really worried."
msgstr "Pero esta vez... estoy realmente preocupada."

msgctxt "236_Haruka"
msgid "It feels like if you go to Tokyo now, you're never gonna\\r\n"\n"come home."
msgstr "Siento que sí vas a Tokio ahora, nunca volverás a casa."

msgctxt "248_Kiryu"
msgid "You heard us talking last night, huh?"
msgstr "Nos escuchaste hablar anoche, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "260_Haruka"
msgid "Maybe you want to know what happened five years ago, but I\\r\n"\n"don't care one way or another. I just want you to be safe."
msgstr "Puede que quieras saber lo que pasó hace cinco años, pero a\\r\n"\n"mi no me importa para nada. Solo quiero que estés a salvo."

msgctxt "272_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't care? Haruka, you lost both your parents in that\\r\n"\n"incident."
msgstr "¿No te importa? Haruka, perdiste a tus padres en ese\\r\n"\n"incidente."

msgctxt "284_Kiryu"
msgid "I lost Nishiki and Kazama-san."
msgstr "Perdí a Nishiki y a Kazama-san."

msgctxt "296_Kiryu"
msgid "If there really was something more going on behind the\\r\n"\n"scenes, wouldn't you want to know what it was?"
msgstr "Si realmente hubiera algo más detrás de\\r\n"\n"escenas, ¿no te gustaría saber de qué se trataba?"

msgctxt "308_Haruka"
msgid "I... I'm happy just being here with you, Uncle Kaz."
msgstr "Yo... Estoy feliz de estar aquí contigo, tío Kaz."

msgctxt "320_Haruka"
msgid "That's all I need. Not the truth... Just you."
msgstr "Lo único que necesito. No es la verdad... Solo eres tú."

msgctxt "332_Kiryu"
msgid "Haruka..."
msgstr "Haruka..."

